### New Features Added
- **Sound Trigger**: A sound notification will play whenever a Buy Signal is generated.
- **In-App Notification**: Users will receive a notification within the app when the Buy Signal is triggered.
- **Toast Notification for Buy Signal**: A brief message will appear on the screen to inform the user of the Buy Signal.  

